addAdvocatedTAOLogos(address,uint256).details: Add `_amount` logos earned from advocating a TAO `_taoId` to its Advocate

params._taoId: The ID of the advocated TAO

availableToPositionAmount(address).details: Return the amount of Logos that are available to be positioned on other
availableToPositionAmount(address).return: The amount of Logos that are available to be positioned on other

mint(address,uint256).details: Create `mintedAmount` TAOCurrency and send it to `target`

params.mintedAmount: The amount of TAOCurrency it will receive

setNameAccountRecoveryAddress(address).details: The AO set the NameAccountRecovery Address

setNameTAOPositionAddress(address).details: The AO set the NameTAOPosition Address

setWhitelist(address,bool).details: Whitelist `_account` address to transact on behalf of others

sumBalanceOf(address).details: Get the total sum of Logos for an address
sumBalanceOf(address).return: The total sum of Logos (own + positioned + advocated TAOs)

transferAdvocatedTAOLogos(address,addres.details: Transfer logos earned from advocating a TAO `_taoId` from `_fromNameId` to the Advocate of `_taoId`

params._fromNameId: The ID of the Name that sends the Logos
params._taoId: The ID of the advocated TAO

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).details: transfer TAOCurrency from other address	 * Send `_value` TAOCurrency to `_to` in behalf of `_from`

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfer ownership of The AO to new address

params._theAO: The new address to be transferred

whitelistBurnFrom(address,uint256).details: Whitelisted address remove `_value` TAOCurrency from the system irreversibly on behalf of `_from`.

params._value: the amount of money to burn
